44:25.096 --> 44:28.499 align:left position:25%,start line:73.33% size:75%
DANNY STRONG,
Actor/Writer/Director: I think
there's a common saying that to
write what

44:28.599 --> 44:30.401 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
you know.

44:30.501 --> 44:36.240 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And I think that that is good
advice for an
amateur writer. But a
professional writer

44:36.340 --> 44:40.578 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
