passionate about.

44:40.678 --> 44:49.654 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
When I was a full-time actor, my
entire existence
was based on waiting for my
agent to call.

44:49.754 --> 44:54.358 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I wrote a script for me to star
in as an actor,
which is a very common thing in
Hollywood,

44:54.458 --> 44:58.663 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
