and get this
movie made without you
attached?"

45:08.973 --> 45:11.509 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
I thought, no, this is my
"Rocky."

45:11.609 --> 45:14.412 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
By the way, that film has still
never been
made, so probably not the best
decision.

45:14.512 --> 45:20.985 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
